PRAYER OF THE APOSTLE PAUL
– 
FULL REVERSE COHERENT SCAN
Codex YHWH (YHYYH) w/ Numerical Letter Differentiation
Numerical Note: YHWH (יהוה) = 26 base. YHYYH variant = 36 intensified (doubled Yod for covenant/redemptive emphasis). Literal root fidelity to Nag Hammadi Coptic/Greek fragments with YHWH framework alignment.

Grant what no angel eye has seen and no archon ear has heard and what has not entered into the heart of man which became the angelic and came down upon the earth and became man. Redeem me from every affliction and bring me into the life of the Father. Grant me the first begotten who is in the Pleroma and the first born of all creation. Grant me the one who was sent that I might understand him and be saved. Grant me the one who is hidden that I might speak of him. Grant me the one who is above every name. Grant me the one who is the truth. Grant me the one who is the life. Grant me the one who is the way. Grant me the one who is the light. Grant me the one who is the resurrection. Grant me the one who is the knowledge. Grant me the one who is the eternal. Grant me the one who is the perfect man. Grant me the one who is the All. Grant me the one who is YHWH.
The grace of the Lord Yeshua the Anointed be with my spirit. Amen.
O Father of the Light who has dominion over the All, hear me. I am the one who has come forth from You. I am the one who has returned to You. I am the one who has known You. I am the one who has been redeemed by You. I am the one who has been sealed by You. I am the one who has received the name from You. I am the one who has put on the perfect man.
